title: DDFP 268: All-NFC West team
itunes:title: DDFP 268: All-NFC West team
description:
Shek, Handsome Hank and Elliot Harrison wrap up the #DDFP "All Division Teams" series by drafting the All-NFC West roster. Will Russell Wilson or Colin Kaerpernick be the quarterback and who gets the nod on a star-studded defense? Plus, the guys rank the best NFL players in the '80s.
